{"sn2.2:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 2.2 ","sn2.2:0.2":"1. Pathamavagga ","sn2.2:0.3":"Dutiyakassapasutta ","sn2.2:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn2.2:1.2":"Ekamantam thito kho kassapo devaputto bhagavato santike imam gatham abhasi: ","sn2.2:2.1":"“Bhikkhu siya jhayi vimuttacitto, ","sn2.2:2.2":"Akankhe ce hadayassanupattim; ","sn2.2:2.3":"Lokassa natva udayabbayanca, ","sn2.2:2.4":"Sucetaso anissito tadanisamso”ti. "}